{"tid":1747531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online玩家大型活動 投票Challenge","createTime":"2019-11-23T09:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T16:19:08.000Z","uid":272805,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e89cf1962691887f3bcbf6cde583f95047728f","tid":1747531,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"遊戲玩法：<br />\n1.去投票，然後Tag 兩位<span style=\"color: gold;\">朋友</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.被Tag 果兩位<span style=\"color: gold;\">朋友</span>要落去投票，然之後再Tag兩位<span style=\"color: gold;\">朋友</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如似類推<br />\n<br />\n備註：<br />\n如果被Tag果位朋友唔係選民<br />\n就少少地捐一舊水俾<br />\n612、星火 或者幫襯黃店，然後再Tag兩位<span style=\"color: gold;\">朋友</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以個活動係<span style=\"color: gold;\">任何</span>人都玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記著聽日記得玩呀<br />\nP牌推唔到<br />\n麻煩<span style=\"color: red;\">推上去</span>俾更多人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃藍是政見，黑白是良知<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n多你一票真係好多<br />\n香港人，<span style=\"color: gold;\">去投票</span>！</span>"},{"pid":"85d7d612c71ec6805bc000d0184715764445fc31","tid":1747531,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezEbiS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezEbiS</a>"},{"pid":"703bbecfd3488bf55d267ac2a5f6120e0a2faebd","tid":1747531,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"喂喂有趣wo"},{"pid":"e855f998a90b883c282d7ad5eed66b2008eb3096","tid":1747531,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"順便借位<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有無發現。<br />\n我地好似忽略